const Form=()=>{
    return(
        <form className="add text-center my-4">
        <label htmlFor="add" className="add text-light">
          Add a new todo:
        </label>
        <input
          type="text"
          className="form-control m-auto"
          name="add"
          id="add"
        />
      </form>
    )
}
export default Form
